{"id": "1437790278240043160", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "1376763322568937562", "author_name": "morimens_15", "author_bot": false, "content": "Indeed lotan’s rouse works like madness", "timestamp": "2025-11-11T13:05:15.184000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1437790322271846460", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "1376763322568937562", "author_name": "morimens_15", "author_bot": false, "content": "可以是可以。但一般来说单个唤醒体我们不会写单人获得力量、疯狂这些。都会写成通俗易懂的语言。我思考了一下，除非单个的唤醒体状态能够和CZN一样清晰展示，否则不适合使用这类和整个玩家队伍的状态一致的语言。\n\nIt can be done. However, we generally avoid using terms like 'gaining Madness' when referring to a single Awakener. We prefer common, easily understandable language. \nI considered it, and unless an individual Awakeners status can be displayed as clearly as CZN's, it's not appropriate to use the type of language that reflects the status of the entire player team.", "timestamp": "2025-11-11T13:05:25.682000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "noted", "emoji_id": "1186296147191546007", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "BennettThumbsUp", "emoji_id": "773345984474120202", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
