{"id": "1437687143815184436", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "138030149584158720", "author_name": "insigible", "author_bot": false, "content": "i think it depends on what Ward Phillips name is/the writer's intentions. There's a few characters with differences from lovecraft lore to make clear they're not 1-1, so if Khlarcus in his own guy and not just a reference, I think it's worth keeping it different, especially if WP's name is different than the original lovecraft version", "timestamp": "2025-11-11T06:15:26.021000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-11-11T06:16:39.892000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1437687261738045461", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "oh <@1376763322568937562> while you're here, one thing someone mentioned that might be worth consideration is that maybe the \"GPT beta\" should be removed from the English selection at game start now that the English localization has progressed so much? It presents a really bad first impression to new players and I think 2nd anniversary will probably come with a pretty big influx of new people, so just a minor change here might help a lot (and also maybe the japanese selection here too if the Altplus translation has already been implemented)", "timestamp": "2025-11-11T06:15:54.136000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1376763322568937562"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1437687261335388160", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1032751, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1402941858606219294/1437687261335388160/image.png?ex=6a323b9a&is=6a30ea1a&hm=df886c3ae515b675ebd5f207875882c9004dbe552f28e9a09a0bf452b6811e9e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1437687464398426173", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 19, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "(also worth noting the significant difference between the term GPT and the terms MTL or GTL)", "timestamp": "2025-11-11T06:16:42.454000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["88644018673582080"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1437687261738045461", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1437687563581259879", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "1376763322568937562", "author_name": "morimens_15", "author_bot": false, "content": "Ahh and another thing...\n\nWe are planning to change the place name 阿库特 from **Acushnet** to **Yakutsk**. (as in, the WoD **Spring in Acushnet**)\n\nThe thing is...\nI just learned from our writers that the big explosion when Sylverster/Leonora woke up is base on the **Tunguska explosion**.\n\nWriters named the place **阿库特** because they read from an article that the explosion happened there. \nThe place name was subsequently translated into **Acushnet** ( **阿库特** in Chinese)\n\nHowever, today we learned that the Tunguska explosion actually happened in 雅库茨克 (Yakutsk), not 阿库特 (Acushnet). The article our writer read was wrong (probably a mistranslation)...\n\nSo... The translation will be changed to fit the narrative, but the CN place name will stay unchanged", "timestamp": "2025-11-11T06:17:06.101000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "noted", "emoji_id": "1408408581556015265", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "celestepray", "emoji_id": "1397414070100951110", "count": 3}, {"emoji": "noted", "emoji_id": "1186296147191546007", "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1437687872672239769", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "I don't know if ChatGPT was actually used anywhere in Morimens but generative AI models like GPT have a BAAD name in the west and a lot of people would prefer to never touch anything that has ever used it", "timestamp": "2025-11-11T06:18:19.794000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1437688043665494097", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 19, "author_id": "88644018673582080", "author_name": "arkaether", "author_bot": false, "content": "got it! I had no idea it was based on that, that helps a lot in understanding the lore", "timestamp": "2025-11-11T06:19:00.562000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1376763322568937562"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1437687563581259879", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
